text: Zamira Myrzabekova (born 12 June 1991) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2010 Asian Games, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Zamira Myrzabekova Photostream zimbio * Zamira Myrzabekova swimswam * Kazakhstan's Zamira Myrzabekova attacks against China's Wang getty Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
